    "segments": [
      {
        "start_time": "0:01",
        "end_time": "0:02",
        "text": "What?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:03",
        "end_time": "0:04",
        "text": "Yes way!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:04",
        "end_time": "0:05",
        "text": "It's time for"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:05",
        "end_time": "0:06",
        "text": "News for Kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:07",
        "end_time": "0:08",
        "text": "News for Kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:08",
        "end_time": "0:09",
        "text": "真的假的!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:10",
        "end_time": "0:11",
        "text": "原來"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:13",
        "end_time": "0:14",
        "text": "是"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:14",
        "end_time": "0:16",
        "text": "你不知道的趣味新鮮事"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:16",
        "end_time": "0:18",
        "text": "ICRT's News for Kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:20",
        "end_time": "0:22",
        "text": "It's Mother's Day this Sunday"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:22",
        "end_time": "0:25",
        "text": "Do something special for your mom this weekend"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:25",
        "end_time": "0:28",
        "text": "這個週末就是母親節"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:28",
        "end_time": "0:31",
        "text": "為媽媽做一些特別的事情吧"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:32",
        "end_time": "0:47",
        "text": "爸爸妈妈教我们许多事情,是我们的老师。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:48",
        "end_time": "0:51",
        "text": "但有个台湾女儿反过来当妈妈的老师。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:51",
        "end_time": "0:55",
        "text": "The daughter is a taekwondo athlete."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:57",
        "end_time": "0:59",
        "text": "She won a medal at the Tokyo Olympics."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:59",
        "end_time": "1:06",
        "text": "她是一位跆拳道运动员,曾经赢得东京奥运奖牌哦!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:06",
        "end_time": "1:16",
        "text": "她的女儿从她爸爸的年龄开始学了跆拳道,现在她是一个成年人,她在教她妈妈这种运动!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:17",
        "end_time": "1:25",
        "text": "她的跆拳道是小时候爸爸教她的,现在长大成人后,换她教妈妈打拳。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:25",
        "end_time": "1:29",
        "text": "The mom is learning taekwondo to lose weight,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:30",
        "end_time": "1:33",
        "text": "but her daughter has bigger plans."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:33",
        "end_time": "1:37",
        "text": "She entered her mom in a big sports competition."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:38",
        "end_time": "1:47",
        "text": "媽媽原本只是想運動減肥,但女兒卻給她驚喜,幫媽媽報名參加一個大比賽。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:47",
        "end_time": "1:53",
        "text": "Last month, we spoke about the 2025 World Masters Games in Taiwan."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:53",
        "end_time": "1:57",
        "text": "The game starts in 8 days."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:58",
        "end_time": "2:01",
        "text": "The daughter entered her mom in these games."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:02",
        "end_time": "2:07",
        "text": "She will compete against taekwondo athletes from around the world."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:07",
        "end_time": "2:13",
        "text": "那就是世界壯年運動會 就在8天後舉行"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:13",
        "end_time": "2:17",
        "text": "媽媽要跟世界各地的選手一較高下"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:18",
        "end_time": "2:21",
        "text": "Both the mom and her daughter are training hard."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:21",
        "end_time": "2:28",
        "text": "他們花很多時間在一起笑笑、學習和分享他們喜歡的運動"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:28",
        "end_time": "2:38",
        "text": "現在兩個人非常認真訓練,也因此花更多時間相處,一起創造特別的回憶"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:38",
        "end_time": "2:41",
        "text": "女兒很開心她可以教她媽媽"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:41",
        "end_time": "2:45",
        "text": "讓我們來祝福她媽媽在世界冠軍遊戲裡"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:47",
        "end_time": "2:54",
        "text": "媽媽在女兒調教之下,現在要參加世界壯年運動會的跆拳道比賽"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:55",
        "end_time": "2:55",
        "text": "Do"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:56",
        "end_time": "2:56",
        "text": "做"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:56",
        "end_time": "2:59",
        "text": "Oh no, Mother's Day is this weekend"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:59",
        "end_time": "3:02",
        "text": "不好了,這週末就是母親節"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:02",
        "end_time": "3:03",
        "text": "What should I do?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:04",
        "end_time": "3:04",
        "text": "我該怎麼辦?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:05",
        "end_time": "3:06",
        "text": "There shouldn't be a problem"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:06",
        "end_time": "3:08",
        "text": "那應該不是問題"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:09",
        "end_time": "3:10",
        "text": "Something 一些東西"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:10",
        "end_time": "3:13",
        "text": "Didn't you give her gifts before?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:14",
        "end_time": "3:16",
        "text": "你以前不是都送她禮物"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:16",
        "end_time": "3:23",
        "text": "我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:27",
        "end_time": "3:31",
        "text": "我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:32",
        "end_time": "3:40",
        "text": "我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,我總是送花,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:43",
        "end_time": "3:45",
        "text": "我總是送花,我總是送花,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:46",
        "end_time": "3:46",
        "text": "我總是送花,我"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:46",
        "end_time": "3:47",
        "text": "I learn slowly"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:47",
        "end_time": "3:49",
        "text": "我学的很慢"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:49",
        "end_time": "3:50",
        "text": "That's ok"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:50",
        "end_time": "3:54",
        "text": "Just buy me the best strawberries you can find"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:54",
        "end_time": "3:55",
        "text": "没关系"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:55",
        "end_time": "3:58",
        "text": "你就买能找到的最好的草莓吧"
      },
      {
